## 2026-04-04 - No inline token value editing
- Item is stale — already implemented. Inline editing fully exists for color, number, dimension, string, boolean, fontFamily, fontWeight, duration, and asset types.
- `canInlineEdit` flag gates inline editing: requires non-group, non-alias token with a simple type and `onInlineSave` wired.
- Color: click on swatch → `ColorPicker` modal inline. Number/dimension: click value span → numeric input with +/- steppers. String/other: click value span → text input. Boolean: click → immediate toggle.

